        "description": "This classic dish comes together in just 30 minutes with a handful of pantry staples. The butterflied chicken breast cooks quickly, then is smothered in a creamy and flavorful sauce and served over angel hair pasta. It's the perfect weeknight meal!",
        "draft_status": "published",
        "facebook_posts": [],
        "id": 4548,
        "inspired_by_url": "https://www.saveur.com/article/Recipes/Classic-Veal-Piccata",
        "instructions": [
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Butterfly each chicken breast. Lay a piece of parchment paper on top and pound to about ¼ inch (6 mm) thick. Season generously on both sides with salt and pepper.",
            "end_time": 31333,
            "id": 41441,
            "position": 1,
            "start_time": 6166,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Cut each breast in half lengthwise so you have 4 pieces of chicken.",
            "end_time": 34000,
            "id": 41543,
            "position": 2,
            "start_time": 32000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Add the flour to a wide, shallow dish. Dredge each piece of chicken in flour, shaking off the excess.",
            "end_time": 38666,
            "id": 41442,
            "position": 3,
            "start_time": 36000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Fry the chicken until golden brown, about 3-4 minutes per side. Remove the chicken from the pan and set aside.",
            "end_time": 53166,
            "id": 41443,
            "position": 4,
            "start_time": 40000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Pour the white wine into the pan and cook until reduced by half, about 1 minute.",
            "end_time": 55333,
            "id": 41444,
            "position": 5,
            "start_time": 54000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Add the butter, garlic, and capers and cook until fragrant, about 2 minutes.",
            "end_time": 69500,
            "id": 41445,
            "position": 6,
            "start_time": 56000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Stir in the lemon juice and chicken stock and cook for 5 minutes, until the sauce has slightly thickened.",
            "end_time": 79666,
            "id": 41446,
            "position": 7,
            "start_time": 70000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Stir in the cream, then return the chicken to the pan.",
            "end_time": 90000,
            "id": 41447,
            "position": 8,
            "start_time": 80000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Sprinkle with the parsley and turn the chicken to coat in the sauce. Simmer for 2 minutes, until the sauce thickens slightly, then remove from the heat.",
            "end_time": 98333,
            "id": 41544,
            "position": 9,
            "start_time": 91000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Serve the chicken and sauce over angel hair pasta.",
            "end_time": 103666,
            "id": 41448,
            "position": 10,
            "start_time": 102000,
            "temperature": null
          },
          {
            "appliance": null,
            "display_text": "Enjoy!",
            "end_time": 109666,
            "id": 41449,
            "position": 11,
            "start_time": 104000,
            "temperature": null
          }
        ],
